data.description: PRICE REDUCED, MOTIVATED SELLERS, BRING OFFERS!! Incredible opportunity to own your own slice of paradise in Suntree Estates on half an acre!!  This executive style custom built home, by Larry Gulledge with Classic Homes, features all the comforts you would expect in Luxury home.  The interior of this home was featured in the popular magazine, SPACES!  ONE OF A KIND ATTACHED AIR CONDITIONED 1400sqft SHOP with plumbing and special filtration for the perfect work area or perhaps a gym or even a mancave as well as a 3 car garage for all your toys, and a turn around driveway!!! 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 full baths, granite counter tops, coffered ceilings, custom cabinetry, dual Trane A/C system, central vacuum, accordion hurricane shutters all the way around, and a large screened in patio/pool area designed for entertaining and take in the beautiful Florida sunsets! Neighborhood has fiber optic already in place!! This meticulously maintained home will not disappoint!!!!!
